dct_title_s: California Department of Forestry and Fire Protection, GIS Maps & Data
dct_description_sm: The California Department of Forestry and Fire Protection's Fire and Resource Assessment Program (FRAP) assesses the amount and extent of California's forests and rangelands, analyzes their conditions and identifies alternative management and policy guidelines
